headline: Truist to speak at the Goldman Sachs 2025 Financial Services Conference
summary: Truist Financial Corporation (NYSE: TFC) today announced that Chairman and Chief Executive Officer Bill Rogers will speak at the Goldman Sachs 2025 Financial Services Conference at 9:20 a.m. ET on Tuesday, December 9, 2025, in New York City.

headline: Truist taps Microsoft alum as AI chief
summary: Pascal Belaud, who will start at the Charlotte, North Carolina-based bank next week, will shape the vision and execution of Truist’s AI, data and advanced automation strategy, the lender said.
